

# 1. Enterprise Knowledge Graph (Biggest Differentiator)

Google:

```
Question

↓

Find matching documents

↓

Answer
```

Avora AI:

```
Question

↓

Documents
Emails
Policies
Jira
GitHub
Slack
SAP
CRM

↓

Knowledge Graph

↓

Reasoning

↓

